{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, I do remember seeing the Germans marching into Hungary because we lived in the main road with this Nazi salute.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other thing that side-- you know, the motor bicycles with the side cars-- if I see any like that, it makes me shiver, because now and then I see a motor bicycle with this sidecar. it's really making me shiver.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It reminds me this-- the start when the Germans arrive to Hungary and all that was arranged to get us out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would never go back to Hungary ever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I really don't understand those Jews who've gone back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really don't know understand them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't like that choice, you see, because I've heard I could learn the language in English easier than any other language, because when we came out the Red Cross took us to a place where was everybody.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They asked name and address, and you know, what job they can do, so they sort them out who is going where.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had not any other job than working in the dressmaking factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I find that to learn any other language than English, it would be difficult.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said I would like to come to England or any English-speaking country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was-- England is where I came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I did mention I have relatives in America, but I couldn't tell the name and address, so they couldn't contact them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It says it was Ohio, but I mean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a big place and how they can find them?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, everybody who had some funny name was most changed it, you know, because Hochhauser is not an easy name to say, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
